				Even though jumping while runningwill give you distance you lose a lot of stamina. Anyone know what stamina affects? The higher your stamina the faster you regain conciousness(spelling?) which means even though you are now 5 feet closer to safety, the stamina you just spent just let you die. DO NOT JUMP WHILE RUNNING!!<BR>
